{"tid":1065390,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"迪麗熱巴 Vs angelababy","createTime":"2019-03-17T08:20:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-17T10:10:55.000Z","uid":232334,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"602dd01e1df7637e852ee24637d571496fe811f3","tid":1065390,"uid":232334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T08:20:42.000Z","msg":"其實baby同熱巴成日俾人拎黎比較<br />\n我個人認為根本冇得比 一個一望就知充滿異國風情<br />\n一個就1/4 混血 <br />\n望落其實baby而家都越黎越吾似混血兒<br />\n純粹係大陸女星入面靠樣貌都發到下圍<br />\n所以其實到底啲人成日拎佢地黎比較啲咩呢？<br />\n講樣貌其實兩個都好靚 要二選一真係好難🤮<br />\n講好戲就緊係熱巴喇<br />\n但係點解熱巴成日俾人講到好有心機 明明係一個好普通單純嘅乖乖女<br />\n吾似范爺呢啲大陸G<br />\n大家點睇baby同熱巴<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/17/161253_e61cdaf10749d45d8ec4d22c3a87c299.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F17%2F161253_e61cdaf10749d45d8ec4d22c3a87c299.png&h=932a5bd4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/17/161400_89efe2316c6b8714e024d9c771e98d35.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F17%2F161400_89efe2316c6b8714e024d9c771e98d35.png&h=0e32f614&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/17/161505_3e1ea02848ba8da1dab88f68724db6c1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F17%2F161505_3e1ea02848ba8da1dab88f68724db6c1.png&h=ce772277&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/17/161555_a61f7953518865e37d27535d1f3357c9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F17%2F161555_a61f7953518865e37d27535d1f3357c9.png&h=2fb3769b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/17/161648_d1582fbc9133d6baa80a02a3104154fe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F17%2